  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">New hope for Zambia&apos;s poorest school children!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Over half a million Zambian children are unable to access conventional education.  Schools of Good Hope project works with 8 of Zambia&apos;s poorest communities, who have set up their own makeshift schools and enables them to provide the good standard of education they desire for their children.  By training the untrained volunteer teachers and providing essential resources we will ensure that Zambia&apos;s poorest children don&apos;t have the poorest education!</narrative>
  </description>
